# Slammer

⚠️ EXPERIMENTAL HARDWARE DIAGNOSTICS PROJECT

Slammer is a Python-based hardware stress testing utility designed for controlled system stability testing, troubleshooting, and performance validation.

## Purpose

This project was created to help evaluate system behavior under load, including:

- CPU stress behavior
- System responsiveness
- Thermal stability
- Crash/freeze conditions
- Hardware troubleshooting scenarios

## Intended Use

This tool is intended for personal lab testing, diagnostics, and educational hardware research only.

Do not run stress testing tools on systems you do not own or administer.

## Skills Demonstrated

- Python scripting
- Hardware diagnostics
- System monitoring
- Troubleshooting methodology
- Test documentation

## Disclaimer

This project is experimental and may cause system instability during testing. Use only in a controlled environment.